  "detailed_description": "Catch My Color is a game that solve puzzled by applying the appropriate colors to the sights of Korea in black and white.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Attractions in korea</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/68bb800d8ae1b2109402466103295e1c.poster.avif?t=1708351309\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/68bb800d8ae1b2109402466103295e1c.webm?t=1708351309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/68bb800d8ae1b2109402466103295e1c.mp4?t=1708351309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The background of the game is a Korean landmark.<br>Discover hidden elements in famous places!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hidden Objects</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/95a84fef3725a1c4da0cdb753e595f1f.poster.avif?t=1708351309\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/95a84fef3725a1c4da0cdb753e595f1f.webm?t=1708351309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/95a84fef3725a1c4da0cdb753e595f1f.mp4?t=1708351309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The game's puzzles are essentially hidden object finds.<br>Use the clues below to help you figure out which places to paint and which colors to use!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hint Tickets</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/2c29cab20677f97ba8a2bccfd33f3876.poster.avif?t=1708351309\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/2c29cab20677f97ba8a2bccfd33f3876.webm?t=1708351309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/2c29cab20677f97ba8a2bccfd33f3876.mp4?t=1708351309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If the clues are too difficult, you can use hint tickets.<br>Get hint tickets by coloring in various parts of the map!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Various Colors</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/458460eb6e828ea9d6891359d2c40faf.poster.avif?t=1708351309\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/458460eb6e828ea9d6891359d2c40faf.webm?t=1708351309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660700/extras/458460eb6e828ea9d6891359d2c40faf.mp4?t=1708351309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It's not necessarily to paint correct color, you can color it you like.<br>Depending on the color you paint, you will be able to see the attraction with a completely new feel.",
